@using TepayLink.Sdisco.Authorization
@using TepayLink.Sdisco.Web.Areas.Admin.Models.Partners
@using TepayLink.Sdisco.Web.Areas.Admin.Startup
@model PartnersViewModel
@{
    ViewBag.CurrentPageName = AdminPageNames.Common.Partners;
}
@section Scripts
{
    <script abp-src="/view-resources/Areas/Admin/Views/Partners/Index.js" asp-append-version="true"></script>
}

 <div class="kt-subheader kt-grid__item">
  
    <div class="kt-subheader__main">
        <h3 class="kt-subheader__title">
            <span>@L("Partners")</span>
        </h3>
        <span class="kt-subheader__separator kt-subheader__separator--v"></span>
        <span class="kt-subheader__desc">
            @L("PartnersHeaderInfo")
        </span>
    </div>
    <div class="kt-subheader__toolbar">
        <div class="kt-subheader__wrapper">
            <button id="ExportToExcelButton" class="btn btn-outline-success"><i class="fa fa-file-excel"></i> @L("ExportToExcel")</button>
            @if (IsGranted(AppPermissions.Pages_Partners_Create))
            {
                <button id="CreateNewPartnerButton" class="btn btn-primary blue"><i class="fa fa-plus"></i> @L("CreateNewPartner")</button>
            }
        </div>
    </div>
  
</div>
<div class="kt-content">
    <div class="kt-portlet kt-portlet--mobile">
        <div class="kt-portlet__body">
            <div class="kt-form">
                <div class="row align-items-center mb-4">
                    <div class="col-xl-12">
                        <div class="form-group align-items-center">
                            <div class="input-group">
                                <input type="text" id="PartnersTableFilter" class="form-control m-input" placeholder="@L("SearchWithThreeDot")" value="@Model.FilterText">
                                <span class="input-group-btn">
                                    <button id="GetPartnersButton" class="btn btn-primary" type="submit"><i class="flaticon-search-1"></i></button>
                                </span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
			</div>
                <div id="AdvacedAuditFiltersArea" style="display: none" class="row mb-4">
                    <div class="col-md-12">
						<div class="kt-separator kt-separator--border-dashed"></div>
					</div>

							<div class="col-md-3">
								<div class="form-group">
									<label for="NameFilterId">@L("Name")</label>
									<input type="text" class="form-control" name="nameFilter" id="NameFilterId">
								</div>
                            </div>
							<div class="col-md-3">
								<div class="form-group">
									<label for="WebsiteUrlFilterId">@L("WebsiteUrl")</label>
									<input type="text" class="form-control" name="websiteUrlFilter" id="WebsiteUrlFilterId">
								</div>
                            </div>
							<div class="col-md-3">
								<div class="form-group">
									<label for="LanguagesFilterId">@L("Languages")</label>
									<input type="text" class="form-control" name="languagesFilter" id="LanguagesFilterId">
								</div>
                            </div>
							<div class="col-md-3">
								<div class="form-group">
									<label for="SkypeIdFilterId">@L("SkypeId")</label>
									<input type="text" class="form-control" name="skypeIdFilter" id="SkypeIdFilterId">
								</div>
                            </div>
							<div class="col-md-3">
								<div class="form-group">
									<label for="CommentFilterId">@L("Comment")</label>
									<input type="text" class="form-control" name="commentFilter" id="CommentFilterId">
								</div>
                            </div>
							<div class="col-md-3">
								<div class="form-group">
									<label for="AffiliateKeyFilterId">@L("AffiliateKey")</label>
									<input type="text" class="form-control" name="affiliateKeyFilter" id="AffiliateKeyFilterId">
								</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-3">
                                 <div class="form-group">
									<label  for="MinStatusFilterId">@L("MinMax") @L("Status")</label>
									<div class="input-group">
										<input type="number" class="form-control m-input" placeholder="@L("MinValue")" name="minStatusFilter" id="MinStatusFilterId"/>
                                        <input type="number" class="form-control m-input" placeholder="@L("MaxValue")" name="maxStatusFilter"  id="MaxStatusFilterId"/>
									</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
							<div class="col-md-3">
								<label for="AlreadyBecomeSdiscoPartnerFilterId">@L("AlreadyBecomeSdiscoPartner")</label>
								<select class="form-control" name="AlreadyBecomeSdiscoPartnerFilter" id="AlreadyBecomeSdiscoPartnerFilterId">
									<option value="-1">@L("All")</option>
									<option value="0">@L("False")</option>
									<option value="1">@L("True")</option>
								</select>
                            </div>
							<div class="col-md-3">
								<label for="HasDriverLicenseFilterId">@L("HasDriverLicense")</label>
								<select class="form-control" name="HasDriverLicenseFilter" id="HasDriverLicenseFilterId">
									<option value="-1">@L("All")</option>
									<option value="0">@L("False")</option>
									<option value="1">@L("True")</option>
								</select>
                            </div>
							<div class="col-md-3">
								<div class="form-group">
									<label for="UserNameFilterId">(@L("User")) @L("Name")</label>
									<input type="text" class="form-control" name="userNameFilter" id="UserNameFilterId">
								</div>
                            </div>
							<div class="col-md-3">
								<div class="form-group">
									<label for="DetinationNameFilterId">(@L("Detination")) @L("Name")</label>
									<input type="text" class="form-control" name="detinationNameFilter" id="DetinationNameFilterId">
								</div>
                            </div>

                </div>
                <div class="row mb-4">
                    <div class="col-xl-12">
                        <span id="ShowAdvancedFiltersSpan" class="text-muted clickable-item"><i class="fa fa-angle-down"></i> @L("ShowAdvancedFilters")</span>
                        <span id="HideAdvancedFiltersSpan" class="text-muted clickable-item" style="display: none"><i class="fa fa-angle-up"></i> @L("HideAdvancedFilters")</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <table id="PartnersTable" class="display table table-striped table-bordered table-hover dt-responsive nowrap">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>@L("Actions")</th>
								<th>@L("Name")</th>
								<th>@L("WebsiteUrl")</th>
								<th>@L("Languages")</th>
								<th>@L("SkypeId")</th>
								<th>@L("Comment")</th>
								<th>@L("AffiliateKey")</th>
								<th>@L("Status")</th>
								<th>@L("AlreadyBecomeSdiscoPartner")</th>
								<th>@L("HasDriverLicense")</th>
								<th>@L("UserName")</th>
								<th>@L("DetinationName")</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  
</div>